quran[5{c,v,t}:
3,149,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, agar tum unn logon ke ishaaron par chalo ge jinhon ne kufar ki raah ikhtiyar ki hai to woh tum ko ulta phair le jayen ge aur tum namuraad ho jao ge"
3,150,( unn ki baatein ghalat hain ) haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah tumhara haami o madadgaar hai aur woh behtareen madad karne wala hai
3,151,"anqareeb woh waqt anay wala hai jab hum munkareen haq ke dilon mein roab bitha den ge, is liye ke onhon ne Allah ke sath unn ko khudai mein shareek ٹ Tehraya hai jin ke shareek honay par Allah ne koi sanad nazil nahi ki unn ka aakhri thikana jahannum hai aur bohat hi buri hai woh qiyam gaah jo unn zaalmon ko naseeb hogi"
3,152,"Allah ne ( taied o nusrat ka ) jo wada tum se kya tha woh to uss ne poora kar diya ibtida mein uss ke hukum se tum hi unn ko qatal kar rahay thay magar jab tum ne kamzoree dikhayi aur apne kaam mein baahum ikhtilaaf kya, aur jounhi ke woh cheez Allah ne tumhe dikhayi jis ki mohabbat mein tum girftar thay ( yani maal ghanemat ) tum apne sardar ke hukum ki khilaaf warzi kar baithy is liye ke tum mein se kuch log duniya ke taalib thay aur kuch akhirat ki khwahish rakhtay thay tab Allah ne tumhe kafiroon ke muqaabla mein paspaa kar diya taakay tumhari azmaish kere aur haq yeh hai ke Allah ne phir bhi tumhe maaf hi kar diya kyunkay mominoun par Allah barri nazar inayat rakhta hai"
3,153,"yaad karo jab tum bhage chalay ja rahay thay, kisi ki taraf palat kar dekhnay taq ka hosh tumhe nah tha, aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam tumahray peechay tum ko pukaar raha tha uss waqt tumhari is rawish ka badla Allah ne tumhe yeh diya ke tum ko ranj par ranj diye taakay aindah ke liye tumhe yeh sabaq miley ke jo kuch tumahray haath se jaye ya jo museebat tum par nazil ho is par malool nah ho Allah tumahray sab aamaal se bakhabar hai"
